query: Can you help me track the progress of our latest product development sprint and ensure that tasks are being completed on time?
response: Sure! We can set up a system using GitHub for managing the tasks and code repositories, Notion for documenting the sprint details and progress, and Slack for real-time communication. We can create GitHub issues for each task, use Notion to track the overall sprint progress, and set up Slack notifications for important updates and deadlines.

metadata.description: Coordinate product development across multiple tools
